nd Sports, Mrs. Ladi Ajene-Isegbe was reassigned to the Ministry of Trade and Investment. According to the Governor, Cooperatives parastatals was removed from the Ministry of Rural Development to make up the new Ministry of Industry and Cooperatives. The Governor also swore in Mr. David Orshi as the new Special Adviser in charge of Project Monitoring and Evaluation. Vanguard News Nigeria By Peter Duru - Makurdi Governor Samuel Ortom of Benue State, Wednesday, effected a minor reshuffle of his cabinet and also created a new Ministry of Industry and Cooperatives. The Governor who announced the shake up in Makurdi also assigned portfolios to two newly appointed Commissioners who two days agoâ€¦ December 23, 2020 In "Politics" Gov. Samuel Ortom on Monday swore in 15 new Commissioners with a charge to bring their experience to bear on the administration. July 22, 2019 In "News" Governor Samuel Ortom of Benue State has appealed to jobless Nigerian youths to fully engage themselves in skills acquisition programmes in order to be equipped to set up businesses of their own to generate wealth and become useful to themselves and the society. December 5, 2017 In "News"